name: Familia Garcia Bows
description: I'm so excited to add a new Exclusive line to the plethora of bows I already make. Lucky Cupcake Originals What makes these bows special? Well I took a few of my favorite things and my favorite memories and made them into a bow! Throughout this line you will see lots Hispanic influence. Pura Cultura. These Bows are made in a 100% cotton fabric. they are light and the colors are vibrant. The 'dingle balls' are just like the ones you would find on the headliners and dash boards of lowriders, add a fabulous feel. The patterns on each bow will vary. I cannot guarantee which colors will pop most. I try to match the dingle balls to the colors that do show. So when you order keep that in mind. You get to pick the dingle Ball Colors.

name: Viva La Raza Bows
description: I'm so excited to add a new Exclusive line to the plethora of bows I already make. Lucky Cupcake Originals . What makes these Bows special? Well I took A few of my favorite things and my favorite memories and made them into a bow! Throughout this line you will see Hispanic undertones. Pura Cultura. These bows were made out of an actual Serape ( mexican blanket). They're heavier than my other bows. They are harder to make as they very easily pull apart when the fabric is cut. Making these the Cadillac of bows. I meticulously put these together. They also feature Dingle Balls. These dingle balls help shape the sides. When you place your order you cannot really choose which color is dominate. Again with the cut of blanket I cannot promise anything. I can promise that this bow is KICK ASS. I also offer this bow with a Virgin Of Guadalupe cap in the middle. I have Several different images. NO two will be alike. I actually have too many images to post. So if you would like one, I will pick one that is super awesome for your bow. The one shown has Yellow dingle balls , Yours will have RED.
